data.description: Welcome to Mission del Lago! This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath family home overlooks the 6th hole of the golf course. The exterior of this home showcases beautiful brick and a 2 car garage. The interior boasts 9' ceilings, granite countertops, tile backsplash, recessed lighting, tankless water heater and much much more! Priced to sell so hurry and make this homes yours!
